name: Alone I Break
description:
Pick me up, been bleeding too long. Right here, right now I'll stop it somehow. I will make it go away. Can't be here no more, seems this is the only way. I will soon be gone, these feelings will be gone. Now I see the times, they change. Leaving doesn't seem so strange. I am hoping I can find where to leave my hurt behind. All this shit I seem to take, all alone I seem to break. I have lived the best I can, does this make me not a man?

Oil, canvas, madness.
